      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver that shows some wear and age but still has usable appeal. The body, paint, trim, and interior all present reasonably well from a distance, though buyers should expect noticeable cosmetic flaws, imperfections, and general signs of use throughout. This is not a show car, but it could make a practical entry-level example for someone comfortable with a vehicle that may need reconditioning and ongoing upkeep.",
