    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical entry point for a buyer who values budget-conscious transportation or a solid project opportunity. It presents as an honest used car with plenty of potential for everyday utility, and it represents strong value for someone looking to keep costs low while still getting behind the wheel. A sensible choice for the right buyer seeking dependable basic transportation at an attractive price.",
