      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance to grab a cheap runabout, project, or handy spare without spending a fortune. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind and could be a smart buy for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a little TLC. If you want honest value and a car with potential, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a tough-running powertrain and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. Starts, runs, and moves out well, with a drivetrain that feels fundamentally sound and a chassis that still does its job. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but for someone wanting inexpensive transportation, a project base, or a practical beater, this one has real value. If you know how to turn a wrench, there\u2019s a lot to work with here.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
